This is a list of women who have been elected or appointed head of government of their respective countries. This list does not include female heads of state , such as president's (See Female heads of state )
List of elected or appointed female heads of government
In the cases of a country being a monarchy a monarch is the head of state (either a King or Queen). All other countries are assumed to be republics where a president is the head of state.
List of elected or appointed female heads of government
United Kingdom , Canada , New Zealand and Jamaica all share the same monarch who is Queen Elizabeth II
